Introduction
------------------------------------------------------------

icb-ws is an experimental HTML5 front-end for Internet CB
Network.

IArchitecture	/projects/Applications/icb-ws/architecture.png	@hostname	@port


Website
------------------------------------------------------------

The front-end consists only of static web pages and scripts.
Set the WebSocket url in modules/config.mjs.

ILogin	/projects/Applications/icb-ws/login.jpg	@hostname	@port
IChat	/projects/Applications/icb-ws/chat.jpg	@hostname	@port


Service
------------------------------------------------------------

The service requires Autobahn. You need at least Python 3.7
to start the service.

  $ python3.7 icb-ws.py -U wss://localhost:7329 \
    -L 127.0.0.1 -P 7329 \
    -s internetcitizens.band -p 7326 \
    --ssl-key localhost.key --ssl-cert localhost.crt


